{"tid":1580811,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"其實有冇社工醫護議員可以開記招證實新屋嶺輪姦事件","createTime":"2019-09-19T09:02:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-20T14:33:24.000Z","uid":181581,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"ffca8a6222556e2421b2b397ff3b321e4605782d","tid":1580811,"uid":181581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T09:02:27.000Z","msg":"假設受害人被滅口<br />\n咁都已經唔需要隱藏事實，因為受害人已經唔存在，可以將所有證據攞哂出黎，如檢查報告，傷口圖片<br />\n所以受害人仲未被自殺<br />\n<br />\n假設受害人仲生存<br />\n咁知情嘅醫護社工係咪都應該開記招親口交代事情，而唔係出對話圖同出post講有輪姦一事<br />\n<br />\n竟然班狗殺人滅口都做得出，咁點解唔先姦後殺去完全毀滅證據，如果受害人係被自殺咁咪同假設一有矛盾<br />\n<br />\n另外強姦係刑事罪行，道德還道德，私隱還私隱，知情不報又算唔算係幫兇"},{"pid":"4cf5301a61f2c075129aad0044f079445db2eb68","tid":1580811,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T09:02:44.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">[公海 文宣 行動整合] 9.29全球抗赤納粹集會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1579667\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1579667</a><br />\n全世界一齊對準ChiNazi極權！</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BZiskWr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBZiskWr.png&h=b85bf973&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">9.29 Global AntiChiNazi 文宣、資訊、行動整合Channel</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/AntiChinazi929\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FAntiChinazi929&d=gqDWnnaI%2FM4dwC7GJUFj5Xs01o1BQ7dYS%2FTJpuaPCiE%3D&h=a769f4c9\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/AntiChinazi929</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>9.29 Global AntiChiNazi 公海</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/NfHvOU5TXSG9DxQIRNkxLQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FNfHvOU5TXSG9DxQIRNkxLQ&d=gqDWnnaI%2FM4dwC7GJUFj5Xs01o1BQ7dYS%2FTJpuaPCiE%3D&h=92bdb9af\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/NfHvOU5TXSG9DxQIRNkxLQ</a>"},{"pid":"508c5f77443a4c0dff1b2b00656c052